cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper is primarily focused on image restoration and denoising using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of graph Laplacian regularization as a trainable module, which falls under the category of machine learning and optimization. Hence, the other likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
